Just finished @Kristen_Arnett's Mostly Dead Things in one sitting... That sitting being outside in my hammock. I've never read a book so equally real and surreal. "Love was a thing that needed constant care. Our intimacy was an uprooted plant, shriveled and withered." 10/10.
I had the chance to hear @Kristen_Arnett read part of her book at UT recently. If you have the chance to see her read, please do! She was so charming and her book is masterfully written.
